<ab facs="#facs_503_r2l5">Dem <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen dar cʒü <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein geleitt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_503_r2l6"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Darnach <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ymmen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
