<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> manns <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> dez
                                <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
<expan>Leitgeb<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wie der bey uns <expan>cze
                                recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, dem <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen dar czü
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein geleitt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; darnach
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ymmen <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sind etlich hynnen gewesen,
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hört</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir die
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch besenden <add>und sie
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan></add> und, wenn ir dann
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> herein kumt, so
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir mit ew davon reden, wie wir das
                        an in <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>Laur<ex>encii.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
